<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="22Feb1918"><font color="red">22 February 1918</font>, <cite>Pound Letters</cite> (Ezra Pound to LR): You will know bynow that there is enough Joyce to use the full installment in March, not stringing it over three issues. That will have helped with the gap you are bewailing.</div>
